settings.step: Take 1-2 tablespoons of Sea Moss Gel.
Enjoy straight from the jar, or mix into your favorite beverage or food. (e.g., smoothies, juice, yogurt, oatmeal).
If mixing, stir until fully dissolved or blended.

settings.title: How much sea moss can I take per day?
settings.description: For general wellness, 1-2 tablespoons (approx. 15-30g) daily is recommended. Adjust as needed based on personal preference and desired benefits.
